Available Tools: add_to_cart | remove_from_cart | update_quantity | get_cart | apply_coupon | checkout
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "product_id": "string", "quantity": number, "coupon_code": "string" }
Response Schema: { "cart_id": "string", "items": [{ "product_id": "string", "name": "string", "quantity": number, "price": number }], "total": number }
---
Question: Put four yoga mats into my shopping cart.
Call: { "func_call": "add_to_cart", "product_id": "YGA-MAT-PRP", "quantity": 4, "coupon_code": null }
Response: { "cart_id": "cart_5501", "items": [{ "product_id": "YGA-MAT-PRP", "name": "Premium Purple Yoga Mat", "quantity": 4, "price": 29.99 }], "total": 119.96 }

Question: Delete one yoga mat from the current order.
Call: { "func_call": "remove_from_cart", "product_id": "YGA-MAT-PRP", "quantity": 1, "coupon_code": null }
Response: { "cart_id": "cart_5501", "items": [{ "product_id": "YGA-MAT-PRP", "name": "Premium Purple Yoga Mat", "quantity": 3, "price": 29.99 }], "total": 89.97 }

Question: I would like to add a stainless steel water bottle.
Call: { "func_call": "add_to_cart", "product_id": "BTL-SSL-BLU", "quantity": 1, "coupon_code": null }
Response: { "cart_id": "cart_5501", "items": [{ "product_id": "YGA-MAT-PRP", "name": "Premium Purple Yoga Mat", "quantity": 3, "price": 29.99 }, { "product_id": "BTL-SSL-BLU", "name": "Insulated Blue Water Bottle", "quantity": 1, "price": 24.50 }], "total": 114.47 }

Question: Take the water bottle out of my cart.
Call: { "func_call": "remove_from_cart", "product_id": "BTL-SSL-BLU", "quantity": 1, "coupon_code": null }
Response: { "cart_id": "cart_5501", "items": [{ "product_id": "YGA-MAT-PRP", "name": "Premium Purple Yoga Mat", "quantity": 3, "price": 29.99 }], "total": 89.97 }

